        " رَسُولُ اَللَّهِ صَلَّى اَللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَ آلِهِ : \"خَيْرُكُمْ خَيْرُكُمْ لِنِسَائِهِ وَ أَنَا خَيْرُكُمْ لِنِسَائِي \"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4538 - The Messenger of Allah (swt) (peace and blessings be upon him and his family) said: \"The best of you is the one who is best to his wives, and I am the best of you to my wives.\""
        ]
      }
